sections.heading: Banks; attempted prevention of possession by department; penalty
sections.text: Any officer, director, or employee of a bank who attempts to prevent the department from taking possession of such bank is guilty of a Class I misdemeanor.SourceLaws 1923, c. 191, ยง 14, p. 445;C.S.1929, ยง 8-184;Laws 1933, c. 18, ยง 46,
